thread.title_full: 2018 Audi SQ5 3.0 TFSI: More Torque without the Supercharger

author: Tony Markovich
title: 2018 Audi SQ5 3.0 TFSI: More Torque without the Supercharger
text:
-The redesigned 2018 Audi Q5 made its debut last year at the Paris auto show, so it was no mystery that a new version of the performance-minded SQ5 variant was on the way; we just didn’t know when. It turns out that when is now. Audi brought out the SQ5 as one of the few surprises at the 2017 Detroit auto show . It arrives lighter, more efficient, and with a new approach to its power by dropping the supercharger. Oh, and it looks a little spiffier as well. READ MORE ››
